This correction rule concerns good-faith overlap in protectable original work. It does not replace ordinary third-party dependency, open-source, asset, or library compliance, which remains governed by the applicable terms for those materials.

This license does not expire. There are no renewal fees, maintenance payments, or lapse conditions. The claim persists for as long as the public record is accessible.

